WEBVTT

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:48.700
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.420 --> 00:00:51.780
=Episode 7=

00:01:02.039 --> 00:01:03.799
Hey man, how much is this car?

00:01:04.399 --> 00:01:05.119
Here for free AC?

00:01:05.640 --> 00:01:06.079
Just sit.

00:01:06.759 --> 00:01:07.719
No need to pretend.

00:01:09.360 --> 00:01:10.760
What makes you think I'm not buying?

00:01:12.599 --> 00:01:13.359
Just look at you.

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:15.079
This car's over a million.

00:01:15.670 --> 00:01:17.000
Ever even seen that kind of money?

00:01:19.959 --> 00:01:20.879
Nice car.

00:01:22.959 --> 00:01:23.640
You, cocky.

00:01:25.519 --> 00:01:26.079
Loser!

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:32.640
C63.

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:35.200
- Hi.
- Hello.

00:01:35.359 --> 00:01:36.400
How can I help you?

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:38.120
Well...

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:40.319
How much is this one going for?

00:01:40.319 --> 00:01:41.920
This is our newest C63.

00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:43.280
It's a little over a million.

00:01:45.700 --> 00:01:46.400
Got one in stock?

00:01:46.400 --> 00:01:47.290
I want to drive it home today.

00:01:50.300 --> 00:01:50.990
I'll pay by card.

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:52.560
Sure.

00:01:52.750 --> 00:01:54.200
I'll start the paperwork right away.

00:01:55.239 --> 00:01:55.920
Wait, hold on.

00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:57.439
There's one more thing.

00:01:58.480 --> 00:01:59.519
Could you do me a favor?

00:02:00.079 --> 00:02:01.439
Please swap the C63 badge

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:02.359
on the back for a C200.

00:02:02.959 --> 00:02:03.480
Got it.

00:02:03.879 --> 00:02:04.719
You like keeping low.

00:02:09.400 --> 00:02:10.480
If you don't hustle today,

00:02:10.799 --> 00:02:12.359
you'll be nothing tomorrow!

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:14.159
- If you don't hustle today,
- If you don't hustle today,

00:02:14.159 --> 00:02:15.960
- you'll be nothing tomorrow!
- you'll be nothing tomorrow!

00:02:19.199 --> 00:02:20.800
From now on, use your eyes.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:22.039
Stop wasting time

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:25.680
on broke guys who'll never close a deal.

00:02:29.639 --> 00:02:30.639
I'm talking about him.

00:02:32.199 --> 00:02:32.759
Hey man,

00:02:33.400 --> 00:02:35.360
did the shop next door kick you out too?

00:02:36.400 --> 00:02:37.159
Sir,

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:38.719
why don't you drive?

00:02:38.719 --> 00:02:39.560
I'll ride.

00:02:39.719 --> 00:02:40.159
It's fine.

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:41.520
Seriously?

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:43.800
It's just a base model C Class.

00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:45.280
Do you even know cars?

00:02:45.439 --> 00:02:46.840
That's the latest C63.

00:02:48.759 --> 00:02:49.960
If you don't hustle today,

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:51.400
you'll be nothing tomorrow.

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:54.879
- If you don't hustle today,
- If you don't hustle today,

00:02:54.879 --> 00:02:56.880
- you'll be nothing tomorrow!
- you'll be nothing tomorrow!

00:02:58.120 --> 00:02:58.719
Stop it!

00:03:11.360 --> 00:03:12.960
Hey pretty, want to hang out?

00:03:14.599 --> 00:03:16.199
Renting a car to impress me?

00:03:17.479 --> 00:03:17.759
I...

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:18.680
bought it.

00:03:19.240 --> 00:03:20.439
Not a rental.

00:03:21.719 --> 00:03:23.159
I bought it just for you.

00:03:23.320 --> 00:03:24.990
Tomorrow we'll
pick up Dong Ruolin in this.

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:27.439
Where'd you get that kind of money?

00:03:28.479 --> 00:03:28.840
It's...

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:31.000
just the base C Class.

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:31.719
Not that pricey.

00:03:31.719 --> 00:03:32.990
That still costs a few hundred thousand.

00:03:34.199 --> 00:03:35.280
I took out a car loan.

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:36.400
So it's free?

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:41.719
Churan, it's time I told you the truth,

00:03:42.530 --> 00:03:43.800
but you can't tell anyone else.

00:03:47.879 --> 00:03:49.039
Actually, I...

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:50.919
won five million!

00:03:51.300 --> 00:03:51.800
The lottery.

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:52.719
It's jackpot.

00:03:57.700 --> 00:03:59.319
(Won 5 Million: Jackpot!)

00:03:59.319 --> 00:04:00.120
Chen,

00:04:00.360 --> 00:04:01.879
I did everything I could.

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:07.080
That's you?

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:09.360
How...

00:04:09.800 --> 00:04:10.879
How is that not me?

00:04:10.879 --> 00:04:11.680
Look at the vibe

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:12.240
and build.

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:13.120
That's totally me.

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:13.960
Ye Chen!

00:04:16.960 --> 00:04:17.879
I just feel like...

00:04:17.879 --> 00:04:18.840
Even if you won the lottery,

00:04:18.840 --> 00:04:21.000
you shouldn't
be blowing money like this.

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:25.439
How is buying my wife a car
blowing money?

00:04:25.439 --> 00:04:26.160
Look at you.

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:27.199
You're the chairwoman now.

00:04:27.279 --> 00:04:28.319
You need a car to match.

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:30.000
Alright then.

00:04:30.279 --> 00:04:31.639
I'll handle the loan payments.

00:04:31.639 --> 00:04:32.390
You don't have to.

00:04:33.020 --> 00:04:33.920
What's yours is yours,

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:35.759
and what's mine is yours too.

00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:38.000
I'll send the rest of the prize money

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:38.639
to you later.

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:39.350
I don't want it.

00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:40.079
Yes, you do.

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:41.990
Just hold onto it for me

00:04:42.079 --> 00:04:43.439
so I don't spend it all on you.

00:04:50.700 --> 00:04:53.700
(Dong Ruolin, Xiao Churan's bestie)

00:04:58.360 --> 00:04:59.839
You've gotten even thinner.

00:04:59.839 --> 00:05:00.480
You're too sweet.

00:05:00.480 --> 00:05:01.079
Ruolin!

00:05:05.079 --> 00:05:05.560
Hai...

00:05:05.759 --> 00:05:06.680
Hailong?

00:05:09.040 --> 00:05:10.319
What are you doing here?

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:12.279
Looks like we're on the same wavelength.

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:13.800
I wanted to surprise you.

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:16.199
Thank you.

00:05:16.839 --> 00:05:17.319
Come on.

00:05:18.079 --> 00:05:19.000
I'll treat you.

00:05:19.480 --> 00:05:21.879
I booked the top restaurant in Jinzhou,

00:05:21.879 --> 00:05:23.040
Weiding Pavilion.

00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:24.560
Weiding Pavilion?

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:27.319
That's impressive.

00:05:27.500 --> 00:05:29.319
I heard it's nearly impossible
to get a table.

00:05:29.480 --> 00:05:30.399
Of course it is.

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:31.639
But I made it happen.

00:05:32.680 --> 00:05:33.360
Mr. Xiao,

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:35.120
could you take me along?

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:36.959
I've never been to a place
that fancy before.

00:05:37.480 --> 00:05:38.560
Do you deserve it?

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:41.399
Hailong,

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:43.800
let's go together.

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:46.680
Alright.

00:05:46.680 --> 00:05:47.959
For Ruolin's sake,

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:49.920
I'll let you two losers tag along.

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:51.680
Alright. Ruolin, let's get in the car.

00:05:53.199 --> 00:05:54.000
What car?

00:05:54.060 --> 00:05:55.890
Don't tell me
you're still riding that e-bike.

00:05:56.879 --> 00:05:58.079
Oh my.

00:05:58.319 --> 00:06:00.279
It's Churan's new ride.

00:06:02.759 --> 00:06:03.360
A Mercedes?

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:04.600
What?

00:06:08.110 --> 00:06:09.680
I thought it was something impressive.

00:06:09.920 --> 00:06:12.920
Turns out
it's just the base model Mercedes C200.

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:14.879
Honestly, it suits you two perfectly.

00:06:15.560 --> 00:06:16.959
Ruolin, come with me.

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:18.879
My car's way faster than that junk.

00:06:19.399 --> 00:06:21.199
How fast a car is depends on the driver.

00:06:21.199 --> 00:06:22.480
Why don't we have a little race?

00:06:22.630 --> 00:06:24.160
Whoever gets to Weiding Pavilion first

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:25.360
will be the winner.

00:06:25.639 --> 00:06:27.240
I don't street race.

00:06:27.519 --> 00:06:29.680
We follow the traffic laws.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:30.720
Whoever gets there first

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:32.040
has real skill.

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:33.340
Sure, let's try it.

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:35.839
Don't cry if you lose.

00:06:36.199 --> 00:06:37.759
Come on, Ruolin, get in.

00:06:39.199 --> 00:06:40.040
Hold on.

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:43.439
Are you scared now?

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:45.079
Without a wager, this is boring.

00:06:45.240 --> 00:06:46.000
Fine.

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:47.040
If you lose,

00:06:47.480 --> 00:06:48.319
get on your knees

00:06:48.720 --> 00:06:50.079
and bow to me.

00:06:50.959 --> 00:06:52.160
You've done it before.

00:06:52.600 --> 00:06:53.360
That's nothing new.

00:06:56.079 --> 00:06:56.399
Stop it.

00:06:56.519 --> 00:06:57.959
What exactly are you trying to pull?

00:07:00.040 --> 00:07:01.279
We'll draw a random challenge.

00:07:03.199 --> 00:07:04.199
Fine!

00:07:26.879 --> 00:07:27.399
Finally here?

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:29.120
Chen,

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:29.839
Churan,

00:07:30.720 --> 00:07:32.000
you got here so fast.

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:34.319
Nice car.

00:07:34.319 --> 00:07:34.839
Ye Chen!

00:07:35.240 --> 00:07:36.519
This is definitely not a C200.

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:38.240
I never said it was.

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:40.120
Are you messing with me?

00:07:40.839 --> 00:07:42.639
Mr. Xiao isn't usually like this.

00:07:42.839 --> 00:07:45.800
Ruolin, let me tell you,
when Mr. Xiao gives his word,

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:46.519
he keeps it.

00:07:46.600 --> 00:07:47.800
He's not the type to back out.

00:07:52.439 --> 00:07:52.879
Fine.

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:55.720
I'll admit I lost today.

00:07:56.120 --> 00:07:56.900
Guess you got lucky.

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:57.839
Let's go, Ruolin.

00:07:59.360 --> 00:08:00.920
Are we doing the random draw or not?

00:08:01.279 --> 00:08:02.160
Of course.

00:08:02.959 --> 00:08:04.879
Let's see what we end up with.

00:08:07.079 --> 00:08:07.439
Hey, man,

00:08:07.600 --> 00:08:08.040
come here.

00:08:10.240 --> 00:08:11.639
I'll pay 500 for a roll.

00:08:11.639 --> 00:08:12.439
Deal.

00:08:15.920 --> 00:08:17.000
How about we light this up?

00:08:18.199 --> 00:08:19.560
It's just firecrackers.

00:08:19.560 --> 00:08:20.199
Leave it there.

00:08:20.360 --> 00:08:21.560
How about we light one?

00:08:22.480 --> 00:08:23.519
Light it inside the car.

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:27.399
Inside my car?

00:08:27.600 --> 00:08:28.360
Can't handle it?

00:08:30.079 --> 00:08:30.800
Hailong,

00:08:31.079 --> 00:08:31.759
maybe forget it.

00:08:31.959 --> 00:08:33.240
Your car's pretty expensive.

00:08:33.480 --> 00:08:35.319
Why don't you just apologize to Ye Chen?

00:08:35.500 --> 00:08:36.800
I'll put in a good word for you.

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:38.080
No need for that.

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:39.600
It's just a car.

00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:41.799
I can afford to lose.

00:08:48.580 --> 00:09:05.720
(Dangerous stunts for drama.
Do not imitate)

00:09:05.720 --> 00:09:06.919
Ye Chen!

00:09:11.120 --> 00:09:12.159
Hailong, you're back.

00:09:12.159 --> 00:09:13.639
Hailong, are you okay?

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:14.399
I'm fine.

00:09:15.240 --> 00:09:16.559
It's just a car.

00:09:16.559 --> 00:09:17.720
I can afford to blow one up.

00:09:18.240 --> 00:09:19.039
Yeah, you're right.

00:09:19.639 --> 00:09:21.080
That's more like it, Mr. Xiao.

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:23.090
As long as you're okay,
that's what matters.

00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:24.720
Why don't we just go eat?

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:26.039
I'm starving.

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:28.159
Yeah.

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:29.399
Let's eat.

00:09:30.770 --> 00:09:31.639
We have a reservation.

00:09:31.960 --> 00:09:33.320
The Gold VIP room.

00:09:33.650 --> 00:09:34.559
You're Mr. Xiao, right?

00:09:34.639 --> 00:09:35.190
You're right.

00:09:36.039 --> 00:09:37.399
I'm Xiao Hailong,

00:09:37.759 --> 00:09:39.840
the son of the Xiao family from Jinzhou.

00:09:41.240 --> 00:09:42.240
I'm sorry.

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:43.799
Since you arrived late,

00:09:43.799 --> 00:09:45.120
your reservation has been canceled.

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:46.279
Please be on time next time.

00:09:49.279 --> 00:09:51.000
I was only a few minutes late.

00:09:51.440 --> 00:09:52.320
I'm sorry.

00:09:52.639 --> 00:09:54.720
That's the rule at Weiding Pavilion.

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:56.080
What rules?

00:09:56.639 --> 00:09:58.000
Those are for normal people.

00:09:58.000 --> 00:09:59.080
Is Mr. Xiao even normal?

00:09:59.360 --> 00:09:59.759
No, wait.

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:01.100
Is he an ordinary person?

00:10:02.440 --> 00:10:04.080
Please don't block the entrance.

00:10:04.200 --> 00:10:05.440
You're holding up other guests.

00:10:05.759 --> 00:10:06.159
Wait.

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:07.960
Mr. Xiao,

00:10:08.559 --> 00:10:09.720
she's gone way too far.

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:10.920
This is too much!

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:11.990
I can't just stand by!

00:10:12.919 --> 00:10:14.000
What do you mean by this?

00:10:14.399 --> 00:10:15.200
I'm telling you,

00:10:15.559 --> 00:10:17.240
I'm eating here tonight

00:10:17.240 --> 00:10:18.200
no matter what.

00:10:18.200 --> 00:10:18.720
No matter what!

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:19.600
Go get your boss out here!

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:20.350
Get him out here!

00:10:22.320 --> 00:10:25.039
Are you sure you want to see our boss?

00:10:25.399 --> 00:10:26.279
Stop wasting my time!

00:10:26.559 --> 00:10:27.440
I already said...

00:10:30.799 --> 00:10:31.840
Wait. Who are you?

00:10:32.240 --> 00:10:34.000
I'm the boss here.

00:10:34.279 --> 00:10:34.799
I'm Hong Wu.

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:37.639
Mr. Hong.

00:10:41.039 --> 00:10:41.519
It hurts!

00:10:41.720 --> 00:10:42.240
Mr. Hong,

00:10:43.039 --> 00:10:44.919
help me teach
some rich punk a lesson later.

00:10:45.240 --> 00:10:46.639
Got it.

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:47.639
Just leave it to me.

00:10:48.679 --> 00:10:49.000
Thanks.

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:53.519
What are you planning now?

00:10:53.960 --> 00:10:55.159
Looks like Xiao Hailong

00:10:55.679 --> 00:10:57.279
really is trying to pursue Dong Ruolin.

00:10:58.600 --> 00:11:00.600
If he actually wins her over,

00:11:00.660 --> 00:11:02.120
with the Dong family's influence,

00:11:02.440 --> 00:11:03.440
Grandma might let him

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:05.679
vie for the chairperson position again.

00:11:05.960 --> 00:11:06.480
So

00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:08.840
I need to kill that possibility

00:11:08.840 --> 00:11:10.120
before it even begins.

00:11:10.440 --> 00:11:12.120
What's all this shouting

00:11:12.120 --> 00:11:13.320
in public?

00:11:13.759 --> 00:11:15.000
Calm down and talk it out.

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:15.960
No need for violence.

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:18.799
You've got some guts, young lady.

00:11:19.279 --> 00:11:19.759
Ruolin...

00:11:19.800 --> 00:11:20.879
Are you standing up for him?

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:22.759
Take her out too.

00:11:23.800 --> 00:11:24.960
She has nothing to do with me.

00:11:24.960 --> 00:11:25.919
She came on her own.

00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:27.399
I'm not with her.

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:29.200
Mr. Xiao,

00:11:29.559 --> 00:11:31.200
that's not very honorable of you.

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:32.399
And you think you are?

00:11:32.399 --> 00:11:34.520
If you're so honorable,
go tell the boss yourself.

00:11:34.559 --> 00:11:35.600
Stop putting on a show.

00:11:37.519 --> 00:11:38.759
Mr. Hong?

00:11:39.440 --> 00:11:40.720
Chen?

00:11:41.840 --> 00:11:42.960
Business looks good.

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:44.000
Just a small operation.

00:11:44.360 --> 00:11:45.639
Nothing special.

00:11:46.600 --> 00:11:48.600
We get by thanks to your support.

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:49.679
You're too kind.

00:11:50.300 --> 00:11:51.240
Let me introduce you.

00:11:51.720 --> 00:11:53.000
This is my wife.

00:11:54.060 --> 00:11:54.799
Nice to meet you.

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:55.880
Nice to meet you too.

00:11:56.519 --> 00:11:57.840
And this is her friend.

00:11:58.840 --> 00:11:59.600
All friends here, huh?

00:11:59.600 --> 00:12:00.399
Yes.

00:12:00.399 --> 00:12:01.240
Just move along.

00:12:02.480 --> 00:12:03.039
Today

00:12:03.279 --> 00:12:05.320
I just wanted to treat them to a meal.

00:12:05.679 --> 00:12:07.720
I hope it doesn't bother you...

00:12:07.720 --> 00:12:08.600
This meal

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:10.000
is on me today!

00:12:11.000 --> 00:12:12.260
Put them in the Diamond VIP room.

00:12:12.279 --> 00:12:12.759
Right away.

00:12:14.039 --> 00:12:14.320
Please.

00:12:14.519 --> 00:12:15.399
Thank you, Mr. Hong.

00:12:18.679 --> 00:12:19.360
This way.

00:12:19.519 --> 00:12:20.159
Let's go eat.

00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:21.820
This way, please.

00:12:26.080 --> 00:12:27.240
What are you doing?

00:12:27.240 --> 00:12:28.039
I'm with them.

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:28.840
Don't touch me!

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:31.480
Ye Chen, what do you mean?

00:12:31.720 --> 00:12:33.039
Ye Chen, what do you mean?

00:12:34.879 --> 00:12:36.679
Trash should stay in the trash can.

00:12:40.279 --> 00:12:41.679
Grandma!

00:12:41.679 --> 00:12:43.620
(Triple Kill)

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:50.000
(How's it going?)
(Everything's on track.)

00:12:50.679 --> 00:12:51.919
(Proceed as planned.)

00:13:13.140 --> 00:13:15.628
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:13:15.715 --> 00:13:19.468
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:13:19.928 --> 00:13:24.865
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:13:25.028 --> 00:13:27.315
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:13:27.628 --> 00:13:30.308
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:13:31.378 --> 00:13:34.003
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:13:34.303 --> 00:13:37.315
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:13:37.515 --> 00:13:40.565
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:13:40.678 --> 00:13:43.640
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:13:43.908 --> 00:13:47.065
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:13:47.290 --> 00:13:51.040
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:53.903
♪I belong to no one♪

00:13:53.965 --> 00:13:57.415
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:13:57.415 --> 00:14:00.090
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:14:00.090 --> 00:14:06.428
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪